::Striker::

Striker looks out the window as the storm begins to break up, the solar 
panels once again gathering energy.

"My team and I came from Cybertron," Striker says, "In a time period after 
most of the others here. We were stationed on a battle cruiser called The 
Maximal Hope. We were flying to relieve a Maximal colony when we picked up a 
transwarp signature of a Predacon vessle. We followed it and ended up here."
